flowRoot.flowPara: The openSUSE Conference (oSC13) will bring together a wide variety of Open Source contributors to collaborate on one of the major Linux distributions.

The sessions at oSC13 cover openSUSE, our technology and the Free and Open Source Software (FOSS) community around us. You can meet many of the people that make FOSS happen, learn from and have fun with them!
